WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 17=

00:01:38.700 --> 00:01:40.010 line:80%
If my guess is right,

00:01:41.370 --> 00:01:42.820 line:80%
you should be Han Yisu.

00:01:43.290 --> 00:01:44.370 line:80%
Elder Han, right?

00:02:00.380 --> 00:02:02.620 line:80%
(Li Sect Elder, Han Yisu)

00:02:02.650 --> 00:02:04.180 line:80%
How did you find me?

00:02:04.620 --> 00:02:06.540 line:80%
The Li Sect folks are useless.

00:02:06.900 --> 00:02:08.650 line:80%
I heard Nie Hengcheng's third disciple

00:02:09.460 --> 00:02:12.140 line:80%
is a master of Gu poison and traps.

00:02:12.780 --> 00:02:15.020 line:80%
There is no other who can

00:02:15.020 --> 00:02:15.860 line:80%
call forth Erosion Ants.

00:02:16.180 --> 00:02:17.740 line:80%
If your father and grandfather

00:02:18.210 --> 00:02:21.180 line:80%
had your courage and wits back then,

00:02:21.500 --> 00:02:22.900 line:80%
things would not be as they are today.

00:02:23.210 --> 00:02:24.650 line:80%
You're just a pawn

00:02:24.650 --> 00:02:26.020 line:80%
Nie Zhe left here.

00:02:26.460 --> 00:02:28.690 line:80%
What right do you have
to judge the Mu clan?

00:02:29.060 --> 00:02:30.900 line:80%
You lost to my aunt back then.

00:02:32.300 --> 00:02:33.180 line:80%
These legs of yours

00:02:33.620 --> 00:02:35.620 line:80%
were cut off by her blade, right?

00:02:36.210 --> 00:02:37.930 line:80%
The 21st Form of the Sunshine Blade.

00:02:38.210 --> 00:02:39.300 line:80%
Sundering Heaven, Slaying Sun.

00:02:40.780 --> 00:02:42.650 line:80%
You're Cai Pingshu's niece.

00:02:42.930 --> 00:02:43.780 line:80%
Yes.

00:02:48.740 --> 00:02:50.650 line:80%
Thank heavens.

00:02:50.900 --> 00:02:52.930 line:80%
Cai Pingshu took my master's life.

00:02:53.300 --> 00:02:54.410 line:80%
And crippled my legs.

00:02:55.180 --> 00:02:57.690 line:80%
She made me live like
a walking corpse for fifteen years.

00:02:58.650 --> 00:02:59.530 line:80%
Today,

00:03:00.690 --> 00:03:03.650 line:80%
I can finally avenge my master!

00:03:06.650 --> 00:03:08.090 line:80%
You think these tiny ants

00:03:09.370 --> 00:03:10.580 line:80%
can really trap me?

00:03:11.530 --> 00:03:13.020 line:80%
You won't make it out alive.

00:03:13.650 --> 00:03:15.340 line:80%
You'll die for sure!

00:03:15.690 --> 00:03:17.490 line:80%
What if I don't?

00:03:34.340 --> 00:03:35.930 line:80%
- Zhao!
- Mr. Mu!

00:03:51.210 --> 00:03:52.050 line:80%
- Mr. Mu!
- Zhao!

00:03:59.060 --> 00:04:00.810 line:80%
Zhao!

00:04:04.900 --> 00:04:06.370 line:80%
Hurry! Move the iron cage away!

00:04:20.210 --> 00:04:21.140 line:80%
Zhao.

00:04:21.140 --> 00:04:21.980 line:80%
Are you alright?

00:04:23.850 --> 00:04:24.690 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:04:26.050 --> 00:04:26.890 line:80%
Where are we?

00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:30.610 line:80%
Beneath the Bliss Palace,

00:04:31.120 --> 00:04:32.210 line:80%
an underground palace indeed.

00:04:45.780 --> 00:04:47.780 line:80%
Tomb of the Mu Couple.

00:04:50.170 --> 00:04:51.380 line:80%
My father told me that

00:04:51.900 --> 00:04:52.940 line:80%
beneath the Bliss Palace

00:04:53.820 --> 00:04:55.140 line:80%
lies an underground palace built by

00:04:55.500 --> 00:04:56.850 line:80%
Mu Donglie, the 5th Chief of Li Sect.

00:04:57.970 --> 00:04:59.820 line:80%
But I never knew he was married.

00:05:00.730 --> 00:05:02.530 line:80%
Why would your ancestor

00:05:02.530 --> 00:05:03.940 line:80%
build an underground palace
for no reason?

00:05:09.050 --> 00:05:10.340 line:80%
His reign was short.

00:05:11.550 --> 00:05:12.580 line:80%
According to sect records,

00:05:13.380 --> 00:05:14.460 line:80%
before he turned twenty,

00:05:15.020 --> 00:05:16.210 line:80%
he handed the Chief's seat

00:05:16.210 --> 00:05:17.610 line:80%
to his nephew.

00:05:17.610 --> 00:05:18.750 line:80%
Then he left and vanished

00:05:18.970 --> 00:05:19.810 line:80%
without a trace.

00:05:20.340 --> 00:05:22.500 line:80%
Seems that ancestor was quite carefree.

00:05:31.210 --> 00:05:32.050 line:80%
Let's go.

00:05:32.500 --> 00:05:34.460 line:80%
Let's check out
the Mu ancestor's underground palace.

00:05:36.140 --> 00:05:39.860 line:80%
(Tomb of the Mu Couple)

00:05:54.820 --> 00:05:55.660 line:80%
Shangguan!

00:05:58.720 --> 00:05:59.730 line:80%
How is the Young Master?

00:05:59.940 --> 00:06:00.780 line:80%
The trap's destroyed.

00:06:00.780 --> 00:06:02.090 line:80%
We can only dig it open manually now.

00:06:02.520 --> 00:06:03.450 line:80%
Have you found Nie Zhe?

00:06:04.050 --> 00:06:04.900 line:80%
Not yet.

00:06:04.900 --> 00:06:06.140 line:80%
We swept the whole palace area.

00:06:06.190 --> 00:06:07.580 line:80%
It's surrounded tight
as a iron fortress.

00:06:07.850 --> 00:06:08.780 line:80%
Where else could he go?

00:06:09.090 --> 00:06:09.930 line:80%
How's the Xuanwu Altar?

00:06:10.380 --> 00:06:11.650 line:80%
Yu Huiyin fled as soon as

00:06:11.750 --> 00:06:13.020 line:80%
she heard the Bliss Palace fell.

00:06:13.020 --> 00:06:14.530 line:80%
The other followers were forced to join.

00:06:15.020 --> 00:06:15.940 line:80%
Once their leader ran,

00:06:16.170 --> 00:06:17.090 line:80%
they surrendered too.

00:06:17.460 --> 00:06:18.930 line:80%
Hurry, dig faster.

00:06:24.850 --> 00:06:27.140 line:80%
Your ancestor's
underground palace is amazing.

00:06:27.610 --> 00:06:29.340 line:80%
It loops endlessly, seamless in design.

00:06:29.720 --> 00:06:31.340 line:80%
We've walked for a long time
and can't get out.

00:06:34.290 --> 00:06:35.140 line:80%
I think this person

00:06:35.900 --> 00:06:37.050 line:80%
was trapped here

00:06:37.320 --> 00:06:38.460 line:80%
and took his own life in despair.

00:06:39.090 --> 00:06:39.930 line:80%
Why did your ancestor

00:06:40.340 --> 00:06:41.340 line:80%
go to

00:06:41.340 --> 00:06:42.530 line:80%
all this trouble?

00:06:42.940 --> 00:06:43.900 line:80%
Did the Demon Sect

00:06:44.380 --> 00:06:46.140 line:80%
have too much money to burn?

00:06:46.700 --> 00:06:47.850 line:80%
Sect records don't say

00:06:48.140 --> 00:06:48.980 line:80%
why Chief Mu Donglie

00:06:49.340 --> 00:06:50.530 line:80%
built the underground palace.

00:06:51.170 --> 00:06:52.410 line:80%
But word in the sect has it

00:06:53.290 --> 00:06:54.650 line:80%
that he left secret manuals here,

00:06:55.020 --> 00:06:55.860 line:80%
along with treasure.

00:06:56.850 --> 00:06:57.690 line:80%
So

00:06:58.090 --> 00:06:59.610 line:80%
these bones are from a treasure hunter.

00:07:02.050 --> 00:07:03.020 line:80%
Forget it.

00:07:03.020 --> 00:07:03.860 line:80%
We're doomed anyway.

00:07:04.290 --> 00:07:05.650 line:80%
Let's sit and rest.

00:07:18.310 --> 00:07:19.250 line:80%
Do you fear death?

00:07:25.090 --> 00:07:26.020 line:80%
Of course I do.

00:07:27.090 --> 00:07:28.290 line:80%
But life is life.

00:07:28.940 --> 00:07:30.140 line:80%
Birth and death are inevitable.

00:07:31.210 --> 00:07:32.050 line:80%
Just accept it.

00:07:35.020 --> 00:07:35.860 line:80%
What about you?

00:07:36.820 --> 00:07:37.660 line:80%
Do you fear death?

00:07:42.920 --> 00:07:44.500 line:80%
I was already a dead man walking anyway.

00:07:45.410 --> 00:07:46.580 line:80%
As long as I kill Nie Zhe

00:07:47.650 --> 00:07:48.820 line:80%
and take back the Li Sect

00:07:49.290 --> 00:07:50.140 line:80%
before I die,

00:07:51.090 --> 00:07:52.530 line:80%
even if we perish together,

00:07:53.700 --> 00:07:54.730 line:80%
I'll never regret it.

00:07:58.460 --> 00:07:59.850 line:80%
I just never thought

00:08:00.820 --> 00:08:01.940 line:80%
you'd actually come.

00:08:05.500 --> 00:08:06.500 line:80%
Now that you're in this world,

00:08:09.020 --> 00:08:10.010 line:80%
I don't want to die anymore.

00:08:28.940 --> 00:08:30.050 line:80%
My ancestor once came here.

00:08:32.310 --> 00:08:33.330 line:80%
Look at this peach blossom.

00:08:33.780 --> 00:08:35.650 line:80%
It has three layers of petals,
from inside to out.

00:08:35.980 --> 00:08:37.930 line:80%
The innermost layer has just two petals.

00:08:38.290 --> 00:08:39.140 line:80%
A signal?

00:08:39.140 --> 00:08:40.020 line:80%
No.

00:08:40.020 --> 00:08:40.900 line:80%
To be precise,

00:08:40.900 --> 00:08:42.050 line:80%
it's a guide from Luoying Valley.

00:08:43.290 --> 00:08:44.140 line:80%
Qian position, three.

00:08:44.690 --> 00:08:45.530 line:80%
Yao position, two.

00:08:46.690 --> 00:08:47.530 line:80%
Follow me.

00:08:57.290 --> 00:08:58.290 line:80%
It's been fifteen years.

00:08:58.860 --> 00:09:00.620 line:80%
Fifteen years,
and it hasn't changed a bit.

00:09:06.170 --> 00:09:07.050 line:80%
I'm truly glad.

00:09:07.740 --> 00:09:08.980 line:80%
It's been so well preserved.

00:09:11.810 --> 00:09:12.900 line:80%
Good, very good.

00:09:16.450 --> 00:09:17.290 line:80%
Elder Yan.

00:09:19.290 --> 00:09:20.130 line:80%
Elder Yan!

00:09:23.620 --> 00:09:26.050 line:80%
We invited you here to
help the Young Master.

00:09:28.650 --> 00:09:29.490 line:80%
The trap closed.

00:09:29.550 --> 00:09:30.490 line:80%
No way to dig it open.

00:09:30.650 --> 00:09:32.290 line:80%
Do you know where it leads?

00:09:32.290 --> 00:09:33.130 line:80%
Any other entrances?

00:09:37.100 --> 00:09:38.220 line:80%
It should be

00:09:38.530 --> 00:09:39.860 line:80%
Chief Mu Donglie's

00:09:40.180 --> 00:09:41.020 line:80%
underground palace.

00:09:41.020 --> 00:09:41.860 line:80%
Underground palace?

00:09:42.100 --> 00:09:42.940 line:80%
What was it for?

00:09:49.690 --> 00:09:50.620 line:80%
I've forgotten.

00:09:50.620 --> 00:09:53.140 line:80%
I need to drink the Bliss Palace's
special wine to remember.

00:09:56.860 --> 00:09:57.700 line:80%
The mechanism's here.

00:10:14.620 --> 00:10:16.740 line:80%
To carve out such an underground world.

00:10:16.950 --> 00:10:18.530 line:80%
That must have cost countless resources.

00:10:19.220 --> 00:10:20.140 line:80%
Was your ancestor idle?

00:10:21.860 --> 00:10:22.700 line:80%
He was far from idle.

00:10:23.620 --> 00:10:25.220 line:80%
He took over the Li Sect at 13,

00:10:25.620 --> 00:10:27.220 line:80%
fought all the way to
Thousandfold Cliff,

00:10:27.750 --> 00:10:28.980 line:80%
nearly wiped out the Six Sects.

00:10:31.410 --> 00:10:33.220 line:80%
Probably just Li Sect bragging.

00:10:36.980 --> 00:10:38.410 line:80%
The carvings on this screen wall

00:10:39.140 --> 00:10:39.980 line:80%
look like storybooks.

00:10:42.300 --> 00:10:43.690 line:80%
It's the story of our founding ancestor,

00:10:44.620 --> 00:10:45.570 line:80%
Mu Xiujue.

00:10:48.050 --> 00:10:50.810 line:80%
(I lived at Thousandfold Cliff
as a child.)

00:10:51.290 --> 00:10:52.690 line:80%
(The world was peaceful.)

00:10:52.690 --> 00:10:53.780 line:80%
(Father raised me strictly.)

00:10:53.780 --> 00:10:55.330 line:80%
(I trained day and night.)

00:10:55.330 --> 00:10:57.220 line:80%
(Demons descended,
harming the innocent.)

00:10:57.650 --> 00:10:59.980 line:80%
(I marched with Father
and fellow disciples from Beichen.)

00:10:59.980 --> 00:11:02.290 line:80%
(Yet the demons were too powerful.)

00:11:02.290 --> 00:11:03.980 line:80%
(We suffered heavy losses.)

00:11:03.980 --> 00:11:05.170 line:80%
(To avenge them,)

00:11:05.170 --> 00:11:07.620 line:80%
(I used forbidden technique
to control demons and fight back.)

00:11:08.450 --> 00:11:10.780 line:80%
(Father was furious,
scolding me severely.)

00:11:11.860 --> 00:11:13.780 line:80%
(We argued for months.)

00:11:13.780 --> 00:11:15.930 line:80%
(Which made him fall ill.)

00:11:15.930 --> 00:11:17.020 line:80%
(I knew I was unfilial.)

00:11:17.020 --> 00:11:18.330 line:80%
(But I didn't think I was wrong.)

00:11:18.980 --> 00:11:21.980 line:80%
(So I left Beichen
and went to Hanhai Mountains alone.)

00:11:23.690 --> 00:11:24.530 line:80%
Oh my god!

00:11:25.380 --> 00:11:27.050 line:80%
He was Beichen Founder's son.

00:11:28.530 --> 00:11:29.570 line:80%
He left in a huff after

00:11:29.720 --> 00:11:30.700 line:80%
a father-son falling-out

00:11:30.930 --> 00:11:31.860 line:80%
and founded the Li Sect.

00:11:32.450 --> 00:11:33.860 line:80%
And our Six Sects' founders

00:11:34.330 --> 00:11:35.380 line:80%
were just six servants.

00:11:38.330 --> 00:11:39.290 line:80%
I told you.

00:11:39.830 --> 00:11:41.410 line:80%
There's no strict line
between good and evil.

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:43.810 line:80%
It's all made-up stories by descendants

00:11:43.810 --> 00:11:44.810 line:80%
with schemes.

00:11:45.450 --> 00:11:46.380 line:80%
Who's good? Who's evil?

00:11:47.530 --> 00:11:48.370 line:80%
No one knows.

00:11:53.170 --> 00:11:54.170 line:80%
Let's check over there.

00:12:19.810 --> 00:12:21.530 line:80%
Did Mu Donglie build this

00:12:22.170 --> 00:12:23.330 line:80%
just to hide a woman?

00:12:23.620 --> 00:12:24.810 line:80%
The tombstone says

00:12:25.290 --> 00:12:26.450 line:80%
"Tomb of the Mu Couple."

00:12:26.860 --> 00:12:27.700 line:80%
Could

00:12:28.170 --> 00:12:29.860 line:80%
they have lived here their whole lives?

00:12:30.220 --> 00:12:32.530 line:80%
Why build a wedding chamber underground?

00:12:34.810 --> 00:12:37.530 line:80%
Does the Li Sect always marry in secret?

00:12:43.020 --> 00:12:43.860 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:12:44.020 --> 00:12:45.100 line:80%
When I marry someday,

00:12:46.350 --> 00:12:47.690 line:80%
I'll announce it to the whole world.

00:13:06.900 --> 00:13:07.740 line:80%
Shiyun.

00:13:08.900 --> 00:13:09.740 line:80%
Luo Shiyun?

00:13:09.780 --> 00:13:11.020 line:80%
This sword belonged to Luo Shiyun.

00:13:11.690 --> 00:13:12.530 line:80%
You know her?

00:13:13.020 --> 00:13:14.740 line:80%
The second-generation demoness
of Luoying Valley.

00:13:15.450 --> 00:13:16.450 line:80%
Extremely talented.

00:13:16.930 --> 00:13:19.290 line:80%
The best swordsman
among the Six Sects back then.

00:13:19.470 --> 00:13:21.330 line:80%
She was supposed to
marry the Lord of Qingque Sect,

00:13:22.050 --> 00:13:23.810 line:80%
but she was tempted by a demon

00:13:24.420 --> 00:13:25.340 line:80%
and ran away with him.

00:13:25.530 --> 00:13:27.380 line:80%
Because of that,
she was branded a demoness.

00:13:27.620 --> 00:13:29.290 line:80%
So that demon was Mu Donglie.

00:13:48.170 --> 00:13:49.330 line:80%
All you Mu clan's are jerks!

00:13:50.140 --> 00:13:52.170 line:80%
Did your clan lock up
my Luoying Valley ancestor here?

00:13:52.590 --> 00:13:53.860 line:80%
What does something 100 years ago

00:13:54.500 --> 00:13:55.500 line:80%
have to do with me?

00:13:55.500 --> 00:13:57.100 line:80%
Can one "Mu" erase another?

00:13:57.780 --> 00:14:00.050 line:80%
Who else am I gonna blame
for your ancestor's dirty deeds?

00:14:08.290 --> 00:14:09.980 line:80%
Today marks the joyful start
of our union.

00:14:11.820 --> 00:14:13.140 line:80%
May we stay together till old age,

00:14:13.570 --> 00:14:14.500 line:80%
our resolve unshaken.

00:14:15.980 --> 00:14:17.170 line:80%
We make this vow.

00:14:18.020 --> 00:14:18.860 line:80%
You and I

00:14:20.320 --> 00:14:21.290 line:80%
never betray each other.

00:14:24.530 --> 00:14:25.680 line:80%
What are you saying?

00:14:30.300 --> 00:14:32.020 line:80%
A marriage contract
between Luo Shiyun and Mu Donglie.

00:14:32.320 --> 00:14:33.250 line:80%
Written by Luo Shiyun.

00:14:35.650 --> 00:14:37.450 line:80%
If they truly loved each other,

00:14:37.900 --> 00:14:39.450 line:80%
why did Mu Donglie lock her up?

00:14:40.380 --> 00:14:41.570 line:80%
If you wish to know the answer,

00:14:43.020 --> 00:14:44.650 line:80%
we'll have to read
Luo Shiyun's handbook.

00:14:47.450 --> 00:14:48.290 line:80%
July 11th.

00:14:48.590 --> 00:14:50.530 line:80%
Mu Donglie has been stationed
at the cliff base for months.

00:14:50.830 --> 00:14:52.020 line:80%
The five sects are too busy to help.

00:14:52.330 --> 00:14:53.170 line:80%
Rescue is hardly possible.

00:14:53.620 --> 00:14:55.530 line:80%
Thousandfold Cliff could fall any day.

00:14:56.100 --> 00:14:57.740 line:80%
So the records were true,

00:14:58.530 --> 00:14:59.500 line:80%
Chief Mu Donglie

00:15:00.020 --> 00:15:01.570 line:80%
almost wiped out the Six Sects.

00:15:01.950 --> 00:15:03.570 line:80%
The Six Sects stood on
the brink of ruin.

00:15:04.290 --> 00:15:05.900 line:80%
Killing the leader Mu Donglie

00:15:06.450 --> 00:15:07.290 line:80%
will save them.

00:15:07.930 --> 00:15:08.900 line:80%
But during the battle,

00:15:09.290 --> 00:15:10.530 line:80%
his men ambushed me.

00:15:10.720 --> 00:15:11.930 line:80%
I slipped and fell off the cliff.

00:15:12.380 --> 00:15:13.410 line:80%
In that perilous moment,

00:15:13.410 --> 00:15:15.450 line:80%
I pulled him down with a silver chain.

00:15:18.700 --> 00:15:21.460 line:80%
(Luoying Valley, Luo Shiyun)

00:15:31.900 --> 00:15:32.740 line:80%
Why?

00:15:32.740 --> 00:15:33.900 line:80%
(Chief of Li Sect, Mu Donglie)

00:15:33.900 --> 00:15:34.900 line:80%
Why didn't you kill me?

00:15:35.330 --> 00:15:36.740 line:80%
This isn't how you should die.

00:15:39.980 --> 00:15:41.530 line:80%
When both our wounds have healed,

00:15:42.900 --> 00:15:43.740 line:80%
we'll duel again.

00:15:43.980 --> 00:15:44.930 line:80%
It's a promise.

00:15:45.840 --> 00:15:47.570 line:80%
♪In days gone by♪

00:15:47.880 --> 00:15:49.430 line:80%
♪Willows swayed gently♪

00:15:49.730 --> 00:15:52.480 line:80%
♪I first saw you in the dimness♪

00:15:53.450 --> 00:15:54.640 line:80%
♪Amid the vast crowd♪

00:15:54.650 --> 00:15:56.120 line:80%
♪A fleeting glance♪

00:15:56.290 --> 00:15:57.200 line:80%
♪And then♪

00:15:57.210 --> 00:16:00.160 line:80%
♪Love consumed me♪

00:16:00.970 --> 00:16:02.520 line:80%
♪Now I think of you♪

00:16:02.920 --> 00:16:04.560 line:80%
♪Snow and rain fall thickly♪

00:16:04.820 --> 00:16:06.160 line:80%
♪Alas, we parted♪

00:16:06.170 --> 00:16:08.360 line:80%
♪Longing for your return♪

00:16:08.490 --> 00:16:09.440 line:80%
♪Moon waxes and wanes♪

00:16:09.450 --> 00:16:10.920 line:80%
♪Letters can't convey my thoughts♪

00:16:10.930 --> 00:16:11.960 line:80%
♪Scattered petals♪

00:16:11.970 --> 00:16:14.200 line:80%
♪Cover the ground♪

00:16:15.060 --> 00:16:17.520 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:16:17.700 --> 00:16:22.380 line:80%
♪Golden wind brushes the jade dew♪

00:16:22.400 --> 00:16:25.120 line:80%
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

00:16:25.380 --> 00:16:29.320 line:80%
♪Wanting to leave yet lingering♪

00:16:30.040 --> 00:16:32.570 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:16:32.850 --> 00:16:37.100 line:80%
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

00:16:37.400 --> 00:16:39.980 line:80%
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

00:16:40.360 --> 00:16:44.700 line:80%
♪Tears are like pearls♪

00:16:45.620 --> 00:16:47.950 line:80%
♪Things stay, yet you're away♪

00:16:48.330 --> 00:16:52.550 line:80%
♪Who will hear the broken strings♪

00:16:53.090 --> 00:16:55.190 line:80%
♪Across the starry skies♪

00:16:55.570 --> 00:17:00.450 line:80%
♪I see your shadow there♪

00:17:00.610 --> 00:17:03.390 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:17:03.390 --> 00:17:07.870 line:80%
♪Golden wind brushes the jade dew♪

00:17:08.120 --> 00:17:10.730 line:80%
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

00:17:11.520 --> 00:17:12.450 line:80%
What's wrong with you?

00:17:13.570 --> 00:17:14.410 line:80%
It's so cold.

00:17:15.610 --> 00:17:18.250 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:17:18.420 --> 00:17:22.790 line:80%
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

00:17:23.120 --> 00:17:25.610 line:80%
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

00:17:26.610 --> 00:17:27.780 line:80%
Don't leave me.

00:17:30.780 --> 00:17:31.620 line:80%
Alright.

00:17:34.380 --> 00:17:36.770 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:17:37.200 --> 00:17:40.450 line:80%
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

00:17:41.970 --> 00:17:44.160 line:80%
♪Such should be♪

00:17:44.830 --> 00:17:54.200 line:80%
♪Our reunion♪

00:18:04.850 --> 00:18:05.690 line:80%
Shiyun!

00:18:08.850 --> 00:18:09.690 line:80%
Yin.

00:18:16.050 --> 00:18:17.330 line:80%
I knew you would still be alive.

00:18:22.850 --> 00:18:23.690 line:80%
Go check inside.

00:18:25.130 --> 00:18:26.090 line:80%
Let's go back,

00:18:27.780 --> 00:18:28.620 line:80%
Yin.

00:18:28.980 --> 00:18:29.940 line:80%
(Qingque Sect, Yin)

00:18:29.940 --> 00:18:30.780 line:80%
Alright.

00:18:47.090 --> 00:18:48.050 line:80%
Soon after,

00:18:48.050 --> 00:18:50.290 line:80%
Yin and I fulfilled our marriage vow.

00:18:50.640 --> 00:18:51.530 line:80%
But unexpectedly,

00:18:51.530 --> 00:18:53.010 line:80%
Mu Donglie came to steal me away.

00:18:53.420 --> 00:18:54.290 line:80%
During the fight,

00:18:54.290 --> 00:18:56.420 line:80%
he ambushed Yin with Chaos Needle.

00:19:04.870 --> 00:19:06.220 line:80%
You've been hit by my Chaos Needle.

00:19:07.050 --> 00:19:07.890 line:80%
Stop struggling.

00:19:09.570 --> 00:19:11.660 line:80%
I hate people
who break their promises the most.

00:19:11.660 --> 00:19:13.180 line:80%
You agreed to stay with me,

00:19:14.420 --> 00:19:17.050 line:80%
but betrayed me
by marrying someone else.

00:19:17.050 --> 00:19:18.050 line:80%
It is you who betrayed me.

00:19:38.290 --> 00:19:39.130 line:80%
Don't!

00:19:41.660 --> 00:19:42.890 line:80%
If you agree to stay,

00:19:44.660 --> 00:19:45.530 line:80%
I'll let him go.

00:19:55.780 --> 00:19:56.810 line:80%
I agree.

00:19:58.330 --> 00:19:59.180 line:80%
Don't harm him.

00:20:06.660 --> 00:20:07.500 line:80%
Die!

00:20:13.330 --> 00:20:14.180 line:80%
I never thought

00:20:14.700 --> 00:20:16.050 line:80%
the ancestors' love

00:20:16.780 --> 00:20:18.330 line:80%
was so thrilling

00:20:18.330 --> 00:20:19.220 line:80%
and touching.

00:20:21.290 --> 00:20:22.370 line:80%
So Zhao,

00:20:23.030 --> 00:20:24.130 line:80%
you like this intense stuff?

00:20:26.740 --> 00:20:27.940 line:80%
Do you think my ancestor

00:20:28.570 --> 00:20:29.940 line:80%
stayed with Mu Donglie

00:20:29.940 --> 00:20:31.520 line:80%
willingly?

00:20:34.130 --> 00:20:34.970 line:80%
Undo it.

00:20:37.290 --> 00:20:38.300 line:80%
This is the underground palace

00:20:39.290 --> 00:20:40.130 line:80%
with a maze outside.

00:20:40.530 --> 00:20:41.660 line:80%
No guide,

00:20:41.660 --> 00:20:42.610 line:80%
no way out.

00:20:43.330 --> 00:20:44.170 line:80%
I'm not leaving.

00:21:25.700 --> 00:21:26.540 line:80%
Stay and eat with me.

00:21:54.120 --> 00:21:56.020 line:80%
I searched for a path
in the underground palace.

00:21:56.020 --> 00:21:57.530 line:80%
Leaving behind the peach blossom mark.

00:21:58.130 --> 00:21:59.370 line:80%
After great hardship,

00:21:59.370 --> 00:22:01.130 line:80%
I finally returned to
Thousandfold Cliff.

00:22:01.610 --> 00:22:03.460 line:80%
But Qingque Sect turned on me,

00:22:03.460 --> 00:22:07.370 line:80%
accusing me of eloping with
the demon Mu Donglie.

00:22:07.940 --> 00:22:09.500 line:80%
Even Yin suspected

00:22:10.050 --> 00:22:11.530 line:80%
I was involved with Mu Donglie.

00:22:12.740 --> 00:22:14.220 line:80%
I was heartbroken,

00:22:15.220 --> 00:22:16.370 line:80%
unable to defend myself.

00:22:16.740 --> 00:22:17.850 line:80%
To prove my innocence,

00:22:19.090 --> 00:22:20.460 line:80%
I jumped off the cliff.

00:22:21.850 --> 00:22:23.780 line:80%
How dare they slander my ancestor!

00:22:24.370 --> 00:22:25.890 line:80%
Typical of them.

00:22:31.460 --> 00:22:32.330 line:80%
But

00:22:32.740 --> 00:22:34.480 line:80%
Mu Donglie saved me.

00:22:35.460 --> 00:22:36.370 line:80%
Why save me?

00:22:36.660 --> 00:22:38.090 line:80%
You already died for them.

00:22:38.500 --> 00:22:39.340 line:80%
You owe them nothing.

00:22:40.090 --> 00:22:40.930 line:80%
Stay here.

00:22:43.290 --> 00:22:44.610 line:80%
Live with me.

00:23:07.570 --> 00:23:10.020 line:80%
If we, like our ancestors,

00:23:11.500 --> 00:23:12.570 line:80%
spent a lifetime here,

00:23:14.640 --> 00:23:15.580 line:80%
wouldn't that be joyful?

00:23:16.220 --> 00:23:17.330 line:80%
Don't you feel

00:23:18.290 --> 00:23:19.700 line:80%
this place is like a cage?

00:23:20.180 --> 00:23:21.290 line:80%
Even if it is a cage,

00:23:22.090 --> 00:23:23.610 line:80%
if I can be with the one I love,

00:23:24.020 --> 00:23:25.290 line:80%
it would still be sweet as honey.

00:23:29.500 --> 00:23:31.810 line:80%
The daughters of Luoying Valley
love the bustle.

00:23:32.980 --> 00:23:34.370 line:80%
Living underground

00:23:34.890 --> 00:23:36.460 line:80%
away from relatives.

00:23:36.980 --> 00:23:38.090 line:80%
How lonely that would be.

00:23:39.130 --> 00:23:40.500 line:80%
Even if she agreed at first,

00:23:41.090 --> 00:23:42.330 line:80%
she'd regret it later.

00:23:43.660 --> 00:23:44.660 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:23:44.660 --> 00:23:45.500 line:80%
remember.

00:23:46.330 --> 00:23:47.890 line:80%
Joy inside a cage

00:23:48.460 --> 00:23:49.740 line:80%
is never true joy.

00:23:50.500 --> 00:23:51.530 line:80%
Where love begins,

00:23:53.090 --> 00:23:54.050 line:80%
it runs deep.

00:23:54.560 --> 00:23:55.610 line:80%
Never bending to setbacks.

00:23:56.180 --> 00:23:58.500 line:80%
If you regret and back out later,

00:23:59.330 --> 00:24:00.460 line:80%
what am I supposed to do?

00:24:02.570 --> 00:24:03.570 line:80%
All I know is,

00:24:03.570 --> 00:24:04.850 line:80%
if we can't find our way out,

00:24:04.850 --> 00:24:05.940 line:80%
we'll starve to death here.

00:24:23.050 --> 00:24:23.890 line:80%
Smells good.

00:24:35.780 --> 00:24:37.050 line:80%
I remember now.

00:24:37.460 --> 00:24:38.420 line:80%
This underground palace

00:24:38.810 --> 00:24:39.980 line:80%
has no exit at all.

00:24:40.460 --> 00:24:42.330 line:80%
I've served as Elder Zhibi

00:24:42.330 --> 00:24:43.170 line:80%
for all these years,

00:24:43.660 --> 00:24:47.370 line:80%
never heard of anyone escaping alive.

00:24:51.920 --> 00:24:52.780 line:80%
For now,

00:24:52.780 --> 00:24:53.850 line:80%
seal all news and

00:24:53.850 --> 00:24:54.690 line:80%
watch Nie Zhe's men.

00:24:54.940 --> 00:24:55.780 line:80%
They're still alive.

00:24:56.370 --> 00:24:57.210 line:80%
Elder Yan,

00:24:57.780 --> 00:25:00.020 line:80%
can you find all historical records of

00:25:00.020 --> 00:25:01.290 line:80%
the underground palace's construction?

00:25:02.180 --> 00:25:03.370 line:80%
You're thinking...

00:25:03.660 --> 00:25:04.850 line:80%
Even a Tomb Chamber

00:25:04.850 --> 00:25:05.810 line:80%
has secret passageways,

00:25:05.810 --> 00:25:06.700 line:80%
let alone an underground palace.

00:25:07.220 --> 00:25:08.060 line:80%
Yes, exactly.

00:25:08.370 --> 00:25:10.660 line:80%
So there must be another exit.

00:25:11.460 --> 00:25:13.850 line:80%
Mu Donglie claimed
he sealed the underground palace,

00:25:14.780 --> 00:25:15.700 line:80%
but I believe

00:25:15.980 --> 00:25:17.290 line:80%
there's definitely another way out.

00:25:17.700 --> 00:25:19.530 line:80%
Otherwise, my ancestral grandmother

00:25:19.530 --> 00:25:22.090 line:80%
wouldn't have left
the guide to Luoying Valley.

00:25:30.500 --> 00:25:31.890 line:80%
There's another guide hidden here.

00:25:47.090 --> 00:25:48.330 line:80%
Now I believe

00:25:48.610 --> 00:25:49.450 line:80%
those two elders

00:25:49.850 --> 00:25:51.000 line:80%
must have left early

00:25:51.320 --> 00:25:52.460 line:80%
and lived happily ever after.

00:25:54.570 --> 00:25:55.410 line:80%
Watch out!

00:26:12.030 --> 00:26:12.970 line:80%
Mr. Mu, are you alright?

00:26:14.020 --> 00:26:15.020 line:80%
Glad to hear you're fine.

00:26:15.020 --> 00:26:16.020 line:80%
His swordsmanship is weird.

00:26:16.420 --> 00:26:17.660 line:80%
I've never seen this style.

00:26:17.940 --> 00:26:19.570 line:80%
No one in the Li Sect
has moves like this.

00:26:20.330 --> 00:26:22.330 line:80%
Could Nie Zhe
have brought the helper outside?

00:26:35.700 --> 00:26:36.850 line:80%
We're finally alive.

00:26:37.500 --> 00:26:38.530 line:80%
Zhao and Mr. Mu

00:26:38.720 --> 00:26:40.290 line:80%
were trapped in
the underground palace so long.

00:26:40.780 --> 00:26:41.700 line:80%
Did anything happen?

00:26:44.460 --> 00:26:45.570 line:80%
It was just a big maze

00:26:46.220 --> 00:26:47.730 line:80%
Wandered around and got out.

00:26:48.530 --> 00:26:49.370 line:80%
And you?

00:26:50.020 --> 00:26:51.740 line:80%
How did you find the exit?

00:26:52.290 --> 00:26:53.890 line:80%
When Shangguan and I
studied old records,

00:26:54.140 --> 00:26:56.460 line:80%
we found a legend about
the Underground Palace construction.

00:26:57.340 --> 00:26:59.210 line:80%
They said the mountain's fengshui
was strange.

00:26:59.520 --> 00:27:00.870 line:80%
The water source dried up suddenly.

00:27:01.330 --> 00:27:02.980 line:80%
And ghosts were said to
wander the woods.

00:27:04.480 --> 00:27:07.020 line:80%
I suspected digging
the secret passageways

00:27:07.020 --> 00:27:08.370 line:80%
cut off the underground water.

00:27:08.990 --> 00:27:10.290 line:80%
So we followed the mountain's terrain,

00:27:10.740 --> 00:27:12.330 line:80%
deduced the palace's layout,

00:27:12.620 --> 00:27:13.890 line:80%
and finally locked onto the location.

00:27:14.290 --> 00:27:15.570 line:80%
If you weren't a young hero,

00:27:15.940 --> 00:27:17.460 line:80%
you could've become a detective instead.

00:27:18.610 --> 00:27:20.740 line:80%
By the way, found Nie Zhe?

00:27:20.740 --> 00:27:22.370 line:80%
We set up checkpoints
all over Hanhai Mountains.

00:27:23.740 --> 00:27:24.610 line:80%
No sign of him.

00:27:32.290 --> 00:27:33.130 line:80%
Mr. Dai,

00:27:33.270 --> 00:27:35.090 line:80%
Shangguan just opened
the Bliss Palace's treasury.

00:27:35.090 --> 00:27:37.090 line:80%
He invites you to
find the Jade Sunflower together.

00:27:39.700 --> 00:27:40.540 line:80%
Thank you.

00:27:45.520 --> 00:27:46.370 line:80%
How is it?

00:27:46.370 --> 00:27:47.220 line:80%
How's the wonton?

00:27:48.370 --> 00:27:49.500 line:80%
Do you think Nie Zhe

00:27:51.220 --> 00:27:53.780 line:80%
dug a secret passageways and ran?

00:27:54.500 --> 00:27:55.570 line:80%
Mu Donglie already turned

00:27:55.570 --> 00:27:57.200 line:80%
the Bliss Palace's underground
into a palace.

00:27:57.660 --> 00:27:58.890 line:80%
Where would he dig another?

00:28:00.530 --> 00:28:01.370 line:80%
Good point.

00:28:02.330 --> 00:28:03.700 line:80%
But I told You Guanyue

00:28:03.700 --> 00:28:05.290 line:80%
to seal all checkpoints.

00:28:05.290 --> 00:28:06.980 line:80%
Even if Nie Zhe could fly,

00:28:06.980 --> 00:28:08.290 line:80%
he can't get out.

00:28:09.890 --> 00:28:11.290 line:80%
So where is he hiding?

00:28:11.660 --> 00:28:13.020 line:80%
From reading

00:28:13.020 --> 00:28:14.370 line:80%
800 storybooks,

00:28:15.090 --> 00:28:16.500 line:80%
people hide in only three places.

00:28:16.820 --> 00:28:17.730 line:80%
The forbidden grounds.

00:28:18.220 --> 00:28:19.060 line:80%
The ancestral shrine.

00:28:19.500 --> 00:28:20.340 line:80%
And under the bed.

00:28:31.330 --> 00:28:33.940 line:80%
This is where my father
lived as a child,

00:28:33.940 --> 00:28:35.500 line:80%
the Mu clan's old residence.

00:28:36.420 --> 00:28:37.610 line:80%
After my grandfather passed,

00:28:37.610 --> 00:28:39.130 line:80%
Father wanted to avoid power struggles,

00:28:39.640 --> 00:28:41.290 line:80%
so he moved to
Huanglao Peak's Carefree Chamber.

00:28:42.320 --> 00:28:44.220 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng refused to
live on Mu Clan lands,

00:28:44.570 --> 00:28:46.530 line:80%
so he built a new palace
at the Bliss Palace.

00:28:48.870 --> 00:28:50.370 line:80%
This became Li Sect's forbidden ground.

00:28:50.820 --> 00:28:52.570 line:80%
The Mu clan is a thorn
in the Nie clan's side

00:28:53.780 --> 00:28:55.020 line:80%
I suppose no one dares come here

00:28:55.890 --> 00:28:56.980 line:80%
to avoid suspicion.

00:29:11.810 --> 00:29:12.650 line:80%
Zhao.

00:29:12.810 --> 00:29:15.530 line:80%
Those 800 storybooks
weren't for nothing.

00:29:26.180 --> 00:29:27.610 line:80%
How dare you hit me?

00:29:28.810 --> 00:29:30.700 line:80%
Uncle Nie, hurry and tell me.

00:29:31.050 --> 00:29:32.890 line:80%
Why did you slaughter Chang Fort?

00:29:33.570 --> 00:29:34.410 line:80%
Why

00:29:34.940 --> 00:29:36.220 line:80%
kill my father?

00:29:38.320 --> 00:29:39.420 line:80%
What's the point of knowing?

00:29:40.130 --> 00:29:41.420 line:80%
What's the point of winning?

00:29:41.420 --> 00:29:42.610 line:80%
You'll be dead soon enough.

00:29:42.850 --> 00:29:43.690 line:80%
True.

00:29:44.020 --> 00:29:46.050 line:80%
So I'll do anything.

00:29:46.530 --> 00:29:48.180 line:80%
Uncle Nie, best you cooperate.

00:29:48.720 --> 00:29:49.690 line:80%
Save yourself the pain.

00:29:49.980 --> 00:29:51.330 line:80%
I'll tell you nothing.

00:29:51.980 --> 00:29:55.090 line:80%
I'll make you die in the dark.

00:29:56.500 --> 00:29:58.330 line:80%
I learned a new martial art.

00:29:59.090 --> 00:30:00.460 line:80%
It's super brutal.

00:30:00.820 --> 00:30:02.610 line:80%
If I channel my inner power
into someone's meridians,

00:30:03.290 --> 00:30:04.500 line:80%
this person will

00:30:05.370 --> 00:30:06.570 line:80%
be unable to live,

00:30:07.290 --> 00:30:08.460 line:80%
nor find release in death.

00:30:14.180 --> 00:30:15.530 line:80%
How does it feel, Uncle Nie?

00:30:15.780 --> 00:30:16.620 line:80%
Speak...

00:30:17.020 --> 00:30:17.860 line:80%
or

00:30:18.740 --> 00:30:19.580 line:80%
not?

00:30:20.130 --> 00:30:21.220 line:80%
Just kill me.

00:30:23.420 --> 00:30:25.460 line:80%
This power will stay in your body.

00:30:26.020 --> 00:30:27.020 line:80%
The pain will get worse

00:30:27.460 --> 00:30:28.300 line:80%
every Chou hour

00:30:29.180 --> 00:30:30.740 line:80%
and Mao hour.

00:30:31.850 --> 00:30:32.780 line:80%
How could Mu Zhengming

00:30:32.780 --> 00:30:34.500 line:80%
have a son so twisted?

00:30:36.460 --> 00:30:37.700 line:80%
I am not like my father.

00:30:38.810 --> 00:30:40.020 line:80%
I can wait with you

00:30:40.740 --> 00:30:41.810 line:80%
till Chou hour.

00:30:54.810 --> 00:30:55.650 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:30:55.810 --> 00:30:56.650 line:80%
What is it?

00:30:56.890 --> 00:30:57.730 line:80%
Madam, she...

00:31:01.050 --> 00:31:01.890 line:80%
Qingyan!

00:31:02.460 --> 00:31:03.700 line:80%
Please forgive your mother.

00:31:04.290 --> 00:31:05.700 line:80%
I was born timid by nature.

00:31:05.700 --> 00:31:07.660 line:80%
It's all that scoundrel Nie Zhe.

00:31:07.660 --> 00:31:09.180 line:80%
He pushed me into a corner.

00:31:09.180 --> 00:31:11.180 line:80%
I had no choice

00:31:11.180 --> 00:31:13.420 line:80%
but to do those stupid things.

00:31:13.420 --> 00:31:16.130 line:80%
I regret it so much, my son.

00:31:16.660 --> 00:31:18.290 line:80%
I was afraid of losing you.

00:31:18.290 --> 00:31:19.330 line:80%
Don't joke, Madam.

00:31:20.570 --> 00:31:23.290 line:80%
You're a spy trained
by the Demonic Camp.

00:31:23.290 --> 00:31:24.420 line:80%
You're not this cowardly.

00:31:24.810 --> 00:31:26.220 line:80%
Even if Nie Zhe

00:31:26.220 --> 00:31:27.330 line:80%
threatened you,

00:31:27.660 --> 00:31:29.050 line:80%
if you really wanted to warn me,

00:31:29.700 --> 00:31:30.780 line:80%
one glance,

00:31:31.330 --> 00:31:32.170 line:80%
one sentence,

00:31:33.090 --> 00:31:34.330 line:80%
you could have found a way.

00:31:34.890 --> 00:31:35.730 line:80%
But you didn't.

00:31:40.130 --> 00:31:41.980 line:80%
If you'd only poisoned me,

00:31:43.290 --> 00:31:44.890 line:80%
I might have let it go.

00:31:44.890 --> 00:31:45.730 line:80%
But

00:31:47.500 --> 00:31:49.610 line:80%
why poison my father?

00:31:52.530 --> 00:31:54.090 line:80%
If you don't tell the truth,

00:31:55.570 --> 00:31:57.290 line:80%
I'll make you taste

00:31:57.610 --> 00:31:59.370 line:80%
the Suzi Fragrance Poison.

00:32:00.530 --> 00:32:01.370 line:80%
Qingyan.

00:32:01.940 --> 00:32:02.780 line:80%
I am your mother.

00:32:02.780 --> 00:32:04.050 line:80%
And I was once your son.

00:32:05.420 --> 00:32:08.740 line:80%
My father was once your husband.

00:32:11.610 --> 00:32:12.700 line:80%
It was Nie Zhe.

00:32:13.570 --> 00:32:15.130 line:80%
He ordered me to kill your father.

00:32:15.850 --> 00:32:17.050 line:80%
Nie Zhe was jealous.

00:32:17.890 --> 00:32:19.090 line:80%
He just became Chief,

00:32:19.550 --> 00:32:21.790 line:80%
yet his skills and reputation
were no match for your father's.

00:32:22.330 --> 00:32:23.940 line:80%
He knew I cared about your father.

00:32:24.620 --> 00:32:25.660 line:80%
Jealousy clouded his mind.

00:32:26.220 --> 00:32:28.020 line:80%
And he kept forcing me into it.

00:32:30.530 --> 00:32:32.700 line:80%
If I didn't poison your father,

00:32:33.810 --> 00:32:35.370 line:80%
he'd have me violated.

00:32:35.980 --> 00:32:37.850 line:80%
I was truly terrified.

00:32:38.290 --> 00:32:39.890 line:80%
I only thought of saving myself.

00:32:41.780 --> 00:32:42.780 line:80%
Qingyan.

00:32:42.780 --> 00:32:44.180 line:80%
I know I was wrong.

00:32:44.740 --> 00:32:46.700 line:80%
I truly know my mistake.

00:32:52.780 --> 00:32:53.620 line:80%
Shangguan.

00:33:01.370 --> 00:33:02.210 line:80%
Chief Nie.

00:33:03.220 --> 00:33:05.500 line:80%
I didn't expect you to be so petty.

00:33:05.500 --> 00:33:07.090 line:80%
Even worse than a woman.

00:33:08.260 --> 00:33:09.180 line:80%
Uncle Nie.

00:33:10.270 --> 00:33:11.460 line:80%
Do you have something to say?

00:33:13.370 --> 00:33:15.610 line:80%
It was your greed for vanity.

00:33:15.610 --> 00:33:17.610 line:80%
You threw yourself into my arms.

00:33:17.610 --> 00:33:19.260 line:80%
If you hadn't shamelessly clung to me,

00:33:19.260 --> 00:33:20.850 line:80%
I'd never have looked twice at

00:33:20.850 --> 00:33:22.980 line:80%
a promiscuous old hag like you.

00:33:26.180 --> 00:33:27.020 line:80%
Liar!

00:33:27.370 --> 00:33:28.660 line:80%
You seduced me first!

00:33:28.670 --> 00:33:29.570 line:80%
Bah!

00:33:29.570 --> 00:33:30.660 line:80%
Who'd seduce you?

00:33:30.660 --> 00:33:32.130 line:80%
You hated Mu Zhengming

00:33:32.740 --> 00:33:34.370 line:80%
for being indifferent to power and fame.

00:33:34.660 --> 00:33:36.420 line:80%
And kept urging me to eliminate him.

00:33:36.700 --> 00:33:38.090 line:80%
Someone like you, who harms her own son

00:33:38.090 --> 00:33:39.370 line:80%
without a trace of mercy,

00:33:39.740 --> 00:33:40.940 line:80%
doesn't deserve to be loved.

00:33:40.940 --> 00:33:42.530 line:80%
What do you mean I urged you?

00:33:42.530 --> 00:33:44.530 line:80%
It was the Man in Black who ordered you.

00:33:44.530 --> 00:33:46.160 line:80%
He told you to attack the Chang Fort

00:33:46.160 --> 00:33:47.050 line:80%
and find something.

00:33:47.050 --> 00:33:47.890 line:80%
Shut up!

00:33:55.290 --> 00:33:56.290 line:80%
Man in Black,

00:33:57.090 --> 00:33:58.020 line:80%
who is he?

00:33:58.020 --> 00:33:59.890 line:80%
There is no Man in Black.

00:33:59.890 --> 00:34:01.500 line:80%
I fought him myself.

00:34:01.500 --> 00:34:03.890 line:80%
Why would he order you to
attack the Chang Fort?

00:34:04.420 --> 00:34:06.090 line:80%
What is he looking for?

00:34:16.780 --> 00:34:18.890 line:80%
If the Man in Black is
really pulling the strings,

00:34:20.780 --> 00:34:22.100 line:80%
I might spare you.

00:34:22.740 --> 00:34:23.930 line:80%
Since he stays silent, I'll speak.

00:34:30.881 --> 00:34:41.541 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:35:00.301 --> 00:35:04.711 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:35:05.276 --> 00:35:09.891 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:35:10.231 --> 00:35:14.796 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:35:15.321 --> 00:35:19.621 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:35:22.566 --> 00:35:27.266 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:35:27.791 --> 00:35:32.081 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:35:32.741 --> 00:35:36.771 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:35:37.086 --> 00:35:42.211 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:35:42.786 --> 00:35:47.596 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:35:47.811 --> 00:35:51.981 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:35:52.706 --> 00:35:56.641 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:35:57.141 --> 00:36:02.416 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

